Diamond's baby mama Zari Hassan has been nominated as the Tanzanian Tourism Ambassador. She took to her social media to announce the good news. "Tourism ambassador Tanzania ni sehemu yangu pia, nikivuta hewa na kukanyaga ardhi yake ndani yangu naona msukumo wa kufanya jambo zaidi," she wrote after attending a Parliament session. "I am excited to be doing something big that will bring more income in Africa." Zari arrived in Tanzania last week for charity work with Softcare diaper company, which she represents as the brand ambassador. She was received at the airport by the Wasafi team led by Diamondâ€™s mother Mama Dangote and Uncle Shamte. During her stay in Tanzania, Zari has been spending at Diamond's mansion in Mbezi Beach with her two kids.